## 📈 Dashboard Features
The Excel dashboard includes:

### Key KPIs
- Total Revenue  
- Total Transactions  
- Average Transaction Value  
- Total Discounts Given  

### Visualizations
- Revenue by Store (Column Chart)
- Monthly Revenue Trend (Line Chart)
- Top Aisles by Revenue (Bar Chart)
- Discount vs Final Revenue (Donut Chart)

### Interactivity
- Store slicer
- Year slicer
- Aisle slicer  

These filters allow users to dynamically explore performance across stores, time periods, and product categories.

---

## 💡 Key Insights
- Certain stores generate higher revenue but rely heavily on discounts
- A small number of aisles contribute a disproportionate share of total sales
- Loyalty customers tend to have higher average transaction values
- Seasonal trends significantly impact grocery sales volume

